w meaning from text using the framework’s built-in word and sentence embeddings, and how to create your own custom embeddings for specific needs."}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2020\/10657","type":"reference","overridingTitle":"Watch Video (41 min)","isActive":true}},"kind":"article","metadata":{"title":"Make apps smarter with Natural Language","role":"sampleCode","roleHeading":"WWDC20","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}]},"references":{"WWDC23.jpeg":{"identifier":"WWDC23.jpeg","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC23.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2020/10657":{"type":"download","url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2020\/10657","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2020\/10657","checksum":null},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC23-10044-Discover-machine-learning-enhancements-in-Create-ML":{"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc23-10044-discover-machine-learning-enhancements-in-create-ml","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Find out how Create ML can help you do even more with machine learning models. Learn about the latest updates to image understanding and text-based tasks with multilingual BERT embeddings. Discover how easy it is to train models that can understand the content of images using multi-label classification. We’ll also share information about interactive model evaluation and the latest APIs for custom training data augmentations."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC23-10044-Discover-machine-learning-enhancements-in-Create-ML","type":"topic","title":"Discover machine learning enhancements in Create ML","kind":"article","role":"sampleCode"},"WWDC20.jpeg":{"alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"WWDC20.jpeg","type":"image"},"doc://WWDCNotes/d